**Counting Even and Odd Numbers with Loops**

**For Loop (Odd Numbers):**
```javascript
var myArr = [];
for (var i = 1; i <= 10; i+=2){
    myArr.unshift(i);
}
console.log(myArr);
```

**While Loop (Even Numbers):**
```javascript
var myArray = [];
let j = 0;
while(j < 10){
    myArray.push(j);
    j+=2;
}
console.log(myArray);
```

**Key concepts:**
- **i+=2:** Increments by 2 (skips every other number)
- **Starting from 1:** Gets odd numbers (1, 3, 5, 7, 9)
- **Starting from 0:** Gets even numbers (0, 2, 4, 6, 8)

